General.Name: Australasian Metals Limited
General.Description: Australasian Metals Limited explores for gold, lithium, and precious metals in Australia. It holds interests in the May Queen and Mt Clermont projects located in Queensland; Fairview project situated in Western Australia; and Mount Peake Pegmatite and Barrow Creek projects situated in Northern Territory. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
